    Client->>gRPC: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC HTTP2 8081 TCP<br/>Encryption: Managed externally
    gRPC->>DP: InferenceServicer to DataPlane<br/>internal function call
    DP->>Model: MLModel.predict<br/>internal function call
    Model-->>DP: Prediction Result
    DP-->>gRPC: InferenceResponse
    gRPC-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over KafkaBroker, Model: Flow 3: Kafka Async Inference - Optional
